nodes.text: Gwynn was a small, portly woman who operated the business Gwynn Dispatch on the planet Elrood. During the Galactic Civil War, a group of Rebel Alliance agents spoke with Gwynn in her office in the city Elrooden while attempting to trace the Rebel operative Shondra Del. Gwynn gave the agents a holographic message that Del had left for them, and she also handed them a business card.
